attributes.action: Ban the sale of real fur.
attributes.additional_details: There is no such thing as ethical fur, animals go through horrific torture, in some cases they are skinned alive.
attributes.background: Some areas, such as Islington, have banned the sale of real fur on public land. The Government should now completely ban the sale of real fur. The majority of the public disagree with the sale of real fur due to the cruelty involved and want it banned.
